<div id="review_938841533" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/938841533" />
    <a title="Nandita Chowdhury" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/31431581-nandita-chowdhury"><img alt="Nandita Chowdhury" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/938841533?book_show_action=true">May 16, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Nandita Chowdhury" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Nandita Chowdhury" href="/user/show/31431581-nandita-chowdhury">Nandita Chowdhury</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780615718255" href="/book/show/22098327-life-of-love">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/31431581-nandita-chowdhury?shelf=romance">romance</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer938841533&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer938841533" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1283270611255148965">I am someone who will go to any lengths to please the love of my life. And I am romantic when it comes to matters of the heart but I simply am no good at reading books. NO offense to the authors who make an attempt to reach the audience but I am not one of their fans. My spouse suggested that I read this book as it reminded him a lot about the way things have been with us in real life. And I had to finally give in and read through these pages. <br/><br/>The first few pages were a harsh reminder of how sad</span>
  <span id="freeText1283270611255148965" style="display:none">I am someone who will go to any lengths to please the love of my life. And I am romantic when it comes to matters of the heart but I simply am no good at reading books. NO offense to the authors who make an attempt to reach the audience but I am not one of their fans. My spouse suggested that I read this book as it reminded him a lot about the way things have been with us in real life. And I had to finally give in and read through these pages. <br /><br />The first few pages were a harsh reminder of how sad it is to read a ‘book’. But the following pages changed the way I think. This book does not have the best language possible, but it has the most heart and I think it will create a wave of magic as and when people get to read through the book. I admit that the romance in my life was rekindled when I put the book down and have started looking at my life in different light. Love is not just about getting what you want, it is more about giving what you have!<br /><br />Way to go Santonu Dhar!<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="1283270611255148965" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


