<div id="review_948992904" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/948992904" />
    <a title="Alyssa" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17635064-alyssa"><img alt="Alyssa" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1483108686p2/17635064.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/948992904?book_show_action=true">May 26, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alyssa" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alyssa" href="/user/show/17635064-alyssa">Alyssa</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780615718255" href="/book/show/22098327-life-of-love">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer948992904" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3120861027473820916">I was thrilled when I received a free copy of this book from the author in exchange for an honest review. First I will say, the story has potential and I did like the ending. However, I felt the whole story was very rushed and the dialogue was very formal and unrealistic. I also would have liked to see more conflict, whether from John&apos;s addictions or even William fighting for what he wants instead of just standing aside. I think that would have made for a more interesting book.</span>
  <span id="freeText3120861027473820916" style="display:none">I was thrilled when I received a free copy of this book from the author in exchange for an honest review. First I will say, the story has potential and I did like the ending. However, I felt the whole story was very rushed and the dialogue was very formal and unrealistic. I also would have liked to see more conflict, whether from John's addictions or even William fighting for what he wants instead of just standing aside. I think that would have made for a more interesting book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3120861027473820916" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


