<div id="review_835856547" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/835856547" />
    <a title="Dwolves13" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6808190-dwolves13"><img alt="Dwolves13" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1379262904p2/6808190.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/835856547?book_show_action=true">Jan 27, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dwolves13" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dwolves13" href="/user/show/6808190-dwolves13">Dwolves13</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer835856547" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8522238656259901501">I was given a free copy of this book in exchange for an honest review. <br/><br/>2.5 / 5<br/><br/>Life of Love, while it is a very sweet and romantic love and it is well written, is lacking a lot of things.<br/><br/>Firstly, things between John and Sarah move too fast. Secondly, I think we don&apos;t have enough information about the main characters. While the relationship between John and Sarah was rushed, the rest of the book was a little bit too slow. A lot of things happened that were not interesting for the main plot and I g</span>
  <span id="freeText8522238656259901501" style="display:none">I was given a free copy of this book in exchange for an honest review. <br /><br />2.5 / 5<br /><br />Life of Love, while it is a very sweet and romantic love and it is well written, is lacking a lot of things.<br /><br />Firstly, things between John and Sarah move too fast. Secondly, I think we don't have enough information about the main characters. While the relationship between John and Sarah was rushed, the rest of the book was a little bit too slow. A lot of things happened that were not interesting for the main plot and I got kind of bored. It was at the very end that things got interesting, although I am not very fond of the ending itself.<br /><br />Anyway, I think this book is enjoyable at the most; however, I am not sure if I will continue reading the trilogy.<br /><br />----------------------<br /><br />2.5 / 5<br /><br />Life of Love es una historia de amor dulce y romántica bien escrita a la que le faltan algunas cosas.<br /><br />En primer lugar, las cosas entre John y Sarah van demasiado rápido. En segundo lugar, no se nos da suficiente información sobre los personajes, lo que hace difícil conocerlos y encariñarse con ellos. La relación de los protagonistas va a toda mecha, demasiado rápido, mientras que el resto del libro va muy muy lento. Además, pasan muchas cosas que no aportan nada a la historia, y hay momentos en que se hace aburrido porque apenas pasa nada. Hacia el final del libro la cosa empieza a animarse, aunque no me ha gustado el final.<br /><br />Sin embargo, se trata de un libro que puede ser entretenido aunque no estoy segura de que siga con la trilogía.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8522238656259901501" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


