<span id="freeTextContainer6501941117439831379">Want to see more bookish things from me? Check out my YouTube channel: <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCferU-BCL2dlFjWdD0rS75Q/videos'>https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfer...</a><br/><br/>I&apos;d like to thank the author Santonu Kumar Dhar for giving me a copy of this book in exchange for an honest review. <br/><br/>I enjoyed this book! It was a love story between &quot;the perfect couple&quot; John and Sarah. Although I felt like their relationship seemed a little bit rushed, it was obvious they were meant to be together. The book was somewhat predictable and I was able to figure out what woul</span>
  <span id="freeText6501941117439831379" style="display:none">Want to see more bookish things from me? Check out my YouTube channel: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCferU-BCL2dlFjWdD0rS75Q/videos">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfer...</a><br /><br />I'd like to thank the author Santonu Kumar Dhar for giving me a copy of this book in exchange for an honest review. <br /><br />I enjoyed this book! It was a love story between "the perfect couple" John and Sarah. Although I felt like their relationship seemed a little bit rushed, it was obvious they were meant to be together. The book was somewhat predictable and I was able to figure out what would happen next. There were a few grammatical errors through out the book but that is to be expected from an ARC copy. The only major problem I had with the book was how formally the characters talked to one another, maybe try to loosen it up a little bit and make it more relaxed in writing.<br /><br />Overall, I would recommend this book to anyone. It is a quick, easy fun read :) Can't wait to read more from this author! Best of luck in the future! </span>
  <a data-text-id="6501941117439831379" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

