      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/5165576.Santonu_Kumar_Dhar">About Santonu Kumar Dhar</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/5165576.Santonu_Kumar_Dhar"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1541348460p3/5165576.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/5165576.Santonu_Kumar_Dhar">Santonu Kumar Dhar
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
36
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11919796109904866210">Santonu Dhar is an author, film producer and entrepreneur. He was born into a Bengali Hindu family on March 28, 1986 in Bangladesh. He has completed post graduation qualification from the Chartered Management Institute (CMI) and he is a fellow of Chartered Management Institute (CMI), UK . Since early childhood, he dreamt of writing stories that readers will fall in love with, but he had to put thi</span>
  <span id="freeText11919796109904866210" style="display:none">Santonu Dhar is an author, film producer and entrepreneur. He was born into a Bengali Hindu family on March 28, 1986 in Bangladesh. He has completed post graduation qualification from the Chartered Management Institute (CMI) and he is a fellow of Chartered Management Institute (CMI), UK . Since early childhood, he dreamt of writing stories that readers will fall in love with, but he had to put this dream on hold to focus on his study and career. Finally, he had got the chance to put pen to paper with his first novel, Life Of Love in 2012, which was first published in 2013. He writes novels with themes that include love, tragedy and fate. <br /><br />He has founded a software company 'Techfast IT Limited' in 2012, he is also founder of many other businesses and currently working as CEO of his company Mahenjo, Inc. </span>
  <a data-text-id="11919796109904866210" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
</div>

